snippet.title: Dealing with Emotional and Stress Eating with Amber Romaniuk
snippet.description:
In this video we talk about:
Challenges of being at home in terms of nutrition, mindset and overall wellbeing
What is stress eating, how can we deal with it right now?
Your daily practices to help maintain a positive mindset and a healthy relationship with food
